sentences.sentence: Click on the icon when you want to print.
sentences.translation: 你想打印时就点击一下这个图标。

sentences.sentence: The print quality of the new laser printer is superb.
sentences.translation: 新激光打印机的打印质量好极了。

sentences.sentence: He started to print his own posters to distribute abroad.
sentences.translation: 他开始印刷他自己的宣传海报以在国外散发。
